          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Reduce Overprescribing Opioids in Treatment Act of 2018 or the ROOT Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits inclusion of pain management questions in a&nbsp;specified health care system survey used by the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services, unless the questions address the risks of opioid use and the availability of non-opioid alternatives. </p>]]></text>
